{"tid":394772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人地死咗個仔走來恭喜 你班連登仔有無良心㗎？","createTime":"2017-09-10T08:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T07:23:56.000Z","uid":57214,"like":132,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f67829b3fbd6fda6852e84a7ff3408a536f37c79","tid":394772,"uid":57214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"乜野「恭喜蔡匪若蓮之子魂歸西天」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班廢青明明都大學生作句字都作得咁樣衰<br />\n唔怪得之俾人取消實習資格<br />\n畢業出來只可以教 Band 3 小學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地死咗個仔唔可以安慰吓人嘅咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隨便一句都可以啦，好似咁：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">驚悉蔡若蓮副局長膝下薨斃<br />\n亟望閣下闔家安康早日團聚</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一家人齊齊整整咁係唔係好好多呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5566e3090c0394ffdd89b5ca1dca32bea03b3624","tid":394772,"uid":57214,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"支共走狗死咗個仔被人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班人就起哂鋼走出來狂嗌禍不及妻兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇來佢地真係好撚驚你地禍佢妻兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明成班撚樣日日係為禍大家家人朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>而家就係明明確確話俾你班走狗聽<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼續為支那為虎作倀<br />\n禍．必．及．家．人</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"56146ed1ba66bb67e979395257e069017ee19318","tid":394772,"uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"有五毛負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b27bbc3feedd41cb5ed2eaebbd051d13ef8ca76","tid":394772,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:09:20.000Z"